primary.context: Caller has two contracts and wants to pay maintenance fees for the West Palm property
primary.detail: The agent identified the correct contract and confirmed sending a payment link via text/email.

secondary.context: First monthly loan payment for new Parkway property
secondary.detail: The agent identified the mortgage contract but the call ended after the primary task was initiated without addressing the mortgage payment.

steps: Caller expressed frustration with previous attempts and requested a representative.
Agent offered automated help to avoid 20-minute wait; caller agreed.
Agent performed account lookup and verified identity (name and state).
Agent identified two separate contracts (Palm Beach and Parkway).
Caller chose to handle Palm Beach maintenance fees first.
Agent confirmed contact info and sent the payment link.

actions.detail: Verified name and state of residence
Sent maintenance fee link for Palm Beach contract

insights.summary: The caller wanted to pay maintenance fees for one property and a mortgage payment for another. The agent successfully verified the account and sent a link for the maintenance fees before the call concluded.
insights.verbatim: I've called several times today. I'm trying to get the virtual agent to help me. I'm trying to pay my maintenance fees.
